  "prompt": "How do I know true love?",
  "response": "Determining whether you are experiencing true love can be complex, as it involves both emotional and psychological factors. Here are some signs that may indicate true love:\n\n1. **Mutual Respect:** True love includes deep respect for each other\u2019s individuality, opinions, and boundaries.\n\n2. **Trust and Loyalty:** Feeling secure and trusting your partner is a fundamental part of true love. You don\u2019t fear betrayal or feel the need to constantly check for loyalty.\n\n3. **Open Communication:** Both partners can express their thoughts and feelings honestly without fear of judgment. You should feel that your opinions are heard and valued.\n\n4. **Empathy:** True love involves understanding and sharing your partner\u2019s feelings and experiences, showing genuine concern for their well-being.\n\n5. **Support and Encouragement:** True love includes supporting each other\u2019s goals, ambitions, and personal growth. Your partner should be your biggest cheerleader.\n\n6. **Sacrifice:** You\u2019re willing to put the needs of your partner above your own sometimes, without feeling resentment.\n\n7. **Consistent Care:** Love is shown through actions, big or small, consistently over time. True love does not waver with temporary moods or conflicts.\n\n8. **Acceptance:** True love involves accepting your partner\u2019s faults and imperfections, without trying to change them too drastically.\n\n9. **Contentment:** Feeling happy and content in your relationship, even during mundane or stressful times, can be a sign of true love.\n\n10. **Shared Values:** Having similar life values and goals can reinforce deep love and connection.\n\n11. **Intimacy:** Emotional and physical intimacy where you feel connected, safe, and desired.\n\n12. **Future Plans:** Thinking about and planning a future together where both partners see each other in long-term scenarios.\n\nRemember, true love can look different for every individual and relationship. It\u2019s essential to reflect on your own feelings and dynamics within your relationship to determine if you\u2019re experiencing true love.",
